Commercial Analysts Company 352 Park Avenue South New York, NY - 10010
Job # 4464 August, 1984
VSLO TRACKING STUDY MAIN QUESTIONNAIRE-
Now, I'd like you to think about all the cigarette brands that come in a shape different from the standard round shape cigarette. Please tell me the names of all the cigarette brands that you can think of that come in a shape different from the standard round shape. (PROBE) Any others? (RECORD ON GRID BELOW UNDER Q. 4a)
And, what brands of cigarettes that come in a shape different from the standard round shape cigarette have you seen advertising for in the past 3 months? (PROBE) Any others? (RECORD ON GRID BELOW UNDER Q. 4b)
5a. Now, I'd like you to think about all the hundred millimeter or longer cigarette brands, that is, those that are longer than King size, that you've ever heard of. Please tell me the names of all of them that you can think of. (PROBE) Any others? (RECORD ON GRID BELOW UNDER Q. 5a)
5%. And. what hundred millimeter or longer brands do you remember seeing advertising for in the past 3 months? (PROBE) Any others? (RECORD ON GRID BELOW UNDER Q. 5b)
(ASK Q. 6 FOR EACH LISTED "A" BRAND NOT MENTIONED IN Q. 4a - 5b)

(ASK Q. 7 FOR EACH LISTED "A" BRAND NOT MENTIONED IN Q. 48 OR Q. 5b, BUT MENTIONED IN Q. 4a, Q. 58 OR Q. 6) (ASK Q. 8 FOR EACH LISTED "A" BRAND MENTIONED IN Q. 4a - Q. 6)
8. And, in the last 3 months, have you tried. . (BRAND) ? How about. . . (REPEAT FOR ALL APPROPRIATE BRANDS) (RECORD ON GRID BELOW UNDER Q. 8)
